Html:
Perhap it is possible to manage variables on reference tag, and specify it on compiler options.<br />
Files like this for exemple:<br />
<pre><code>/// &lt;reference path=&quot;{pathProjectA}/Foo.ts&quot; /&gt;
/// &lt;reference path=&quot;{pathProjectB}/Bar.ts&quot; /&gt;</code></pre>

with compiler like this:<br />
<pre><code>tsc ... --var pathProjectA=... pathProjectB=...</code></pre>
